artments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20in%20the%20quickly%20evolving%20AI%20landscape%2C%20there's%20a%20lack%20of%20clarity%20over%20how%20employers%20and%20job%20platforms%20view%20candidates'%20use%20of%20these%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d30b7b58-7f1f-48fe-9fc7-32f0dbe6b8c4%5C%22%3EAutomating%20the%20job%20search%20process%20can%20save%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFederico%20Elia%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faihawk-applies-jobs-for-you-linkedin-risks-inaccuracies-mistakes-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreated%20AIHawk%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0earlier%C2%A0this%20year%2C%20and%20in%20August%2C%20he%20published%20the%20code%20hosting%20platform%20GitHub%20so%20anyone%20could%20use%20the%20tool.%20AIHawk%20automates%20the%20application%20process%20for%20LinkedIn's%20easy-apply%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20which%20pulls%20info%20from%20a%20user's%20profile%20to%20fill%20in%20an%20application.%20To%20date%2C%20AIHawk%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bstarred%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20or%20bookmarked%20%E2%80%94%20on%20GitHub%20by%20more%20than%2022%2C000%20people%20globally.%20There%20are%20more%20than%206%2C300%20members%20of%20the%20AIHawk%20community%20on%20the%20messaging%20service%20Telegram%2C%20where%20users%20critique%20the%20tool%2C%20share%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20use%20it%2C%20and%20provide%20updates%20on%20their%20job%20searches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAIHawk%20is%20one%20of%20many%20AI%20job%20application%20tools%20on%20the%20market.%20While%20it%20can%20be%20installed%20and%20used%20without%20any%20cost%2C%20users%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20doing%20so%20requires%20some%20familiarity%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-python%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprogramming%20language%20Python%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuilherme's%20tech%20background%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20use%20the%20tool.%20He%20said%20AIHawk%20typically%20applied%20to%20about%205