Management%20and%20Budget%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRequiring%20federal%20employees%20to%20come%20to%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week%20would%20result%20in%20a%20wave%20of%20voluntary%20terminations%20that%20we%20welcome%3A%20If%20federal%20employees%20don't%20want%20to%20show%20up%2C%20American%20taxpayers%20shouldn't%20pay%20them%20for%20the%20Covid-era%20privilege%20of%20staying%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20and%20Ramaswamy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fopinion%2Fmusk-and-ramaswamy-the-doge-plan-to-reform-government-supreme-court-guidance-end-executive-power-grab-fa51c020%3Fst%3DYNHNeR%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20their%20cost%20cutting%20plans%20in%20a%20recent%20op-ed%20in%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Hughes%2C%20a%20Trump-Vance%20transition%20spokesman%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20administration%20%26quot%3Bwill%20have%20a%20place%20for%20people%20serving%20in%20government%20who%20are%20committed%20to%20defending%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20American%20people%2C%20putting%20America%20first%2C%20and%20ensuring%20the%20best%20use%20of%20working%20men%20and%20women's%20tax%20dollars.%26quot%3B%20He%20didn't%20offer%20any%20details%20on%20potential%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoriano%2C%20the%20National%20Science%20Foundation%20program%20director%2C%20said%20government%20workers%20were%20%26quot%3Bstill%20scared.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20five%20colleagues%20he's%20spoken%20to%20are%20actively%20seeking%20new%20jobs%20or%20opting%20to%20retire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22358b443d-8060-423e-839f-7f50e6cd8fcc%5C%22%3EIncreased%20efficiency%20is%20a%20welcomed%20idea.%20In-office%20mandates%2C%20not%20so%20much.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrimming%20government%20spending%20and%20improving%20efficiency%20is%20an%20idea%20often%20discussed%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-elon-musk-cutting-federal-spending-could-work-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Ronald%20Reagan%20pursued%20a%20similar%20goal%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Grace%20Commission%2C%20a%20team%20of%20160%20private-sector%20executives%20who%20proposed%20more%20than%202%2C000%20cost-cutting%20measures.%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%20also%20attempted%20to%20reduce%20federal%20spending%20and%20improve%20government%20efficiency%20with%20the%20National%20Performance%20Review%2C%20led%20by%20federal%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20efforts%20had%20mixed%20results.%20Many%20proposals%20from%20the%20Grace%20Commission%20that%20relied%20on%20congressional%20acts%20didn't%20end%20up%20happening%2C%20while%20executive%20orders%20were%20successful%20in%20reducing%20the%20head%20count%20of%20federal%20workers.%20Clinton's%20panel%20similarly%20succeeded%20in%20cutting%20300%2C000%20federal%20workers%20but%20only%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20quarter%20of%20proposals%20that%20required%20legislative%20action%20through%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20operations%20manager%20at%20the%20US%20Postal%20Service%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20the%20department%20for%2027%20years%20told%20BI%20that%20every%20company%20has%20inefficiencies%20and%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20what%20we%20all%20strive%20to%20decrease.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20has%20concerns%20about%20people%20stepping%20in%20to%20make%20suggestions%20for%20the%20Postal%20Service%20without%20having%20%26quot%3Btribal%20knowledge%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20just%20going%20to%20be%20appointed%20to%20this%20type%20of%20commission%20or%20committee%20with%20no%20knowledge%20of%20what%20exactly%20the%20Postal%20Service%20does%2C%20then%20that%20could%20potentially%20be%20a%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDOGE's%20intent%20to%20eliminate%20remote%20work%20is%20also%20a%20concern%20for%20some%20workers.%20The%20HUD%20employee%2C%20who%20had%20been%20working%20remotely%2C%20said%20return-to-office%20enforcement%20would%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%26quot%3B%20be%20enough%20to%20cause%20them%20to%20resign.%20They're%20preparing%20for%20the%20potential%20of%20layoffs%20under%20DOGE%20by%20looking%20at%20other%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20and%20said%20their%20colleagues%20at%20HUD%20are%20taking%20similar%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoyce%20Howell%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%20%E2%80%94%20who's%20been%20at%20the%20agency%20for%20over%2031%20years%20and%20serves%20as%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20its%20AFGE%20union%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20the%20incoming%20administration%20has%20stoked%20concern%20about%20layoffs%20at%20the%20EPA%20and%20fears%20that%20its%20mission%20could%20be%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20town%20halls%20once%20a%20month%2C%20and%20we've%20actually%20broken%20our%20Zoom%20account%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20of%20people%20attending%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20union%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20and%20Ramaswamy%20wrote%20in%20the%20Journal%20op-ed%20that%20the%20commission%20would%20target%20more%20than%20%24500%20billion%20in%20what%20they%20called%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eunauthorized%20government%20spending.%20They%20said%20federal%20employees%20who%20were%20laid%20off%20would%20be%20offered%20early%20retirement%20and%20severance%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20at%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20said%20that%20it's%20not%20that%20easy%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20here%20to%20support%20a%20mission.%20We%20have%20families%20to%20feed%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20as%20easy%20as%20just%20quitting%20our%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FDA%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20normal%2C%20everyday%20people%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0we're%20being%20portrayed%20as%20inefficient%2C%20lazy%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FDA%20worker%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20they're%20coming%20for%20us%20just%20for%20their%20own%20agenda%2C%20not%20realizing%20that%20we're%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20federal%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20federal%20government%20lifer%20said%20that%20many%20workers%20like%20them%20%E2%80%94%20people%20who%20have%20been%20there%20for%20years%20%E2%80%94%20are%20nervous%20they%20might%20be%20the%20first%20to%20go.%20The%20career%20tenure%20of%20a%20median%20federal%20government%20worker%20was%206.5%20years%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fnews.release%2Ftenure.t05.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20well%20above%20the%20median%203.5%20years%20private%20workers%20have%20spent%20in%20their%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20senior%20official%20at%20the%20Commerce%20Department%20told%20BI%20they%20anticipate%20a%20civil%20servant%20brain%20drain.%20%26quot%3BThe%20scientists%20are%20the%20most%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said%2C%20with%20those%20in%20climate%2C%20meteorology%2C%20and%20environmental%20science%20particularly%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20has%20been%20singled%20out%20as%20an%20entire%20agency%20that%20could%20be%20on%20the%20chopping%20block.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheria%20Smith%2C%20president%20of%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAFGE%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eunion%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20and%20a%20civil%20rights%20attorney%20at%20the%20agency%2C%20said%20that%20department%20elimination%20was%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20lower%20end%20of%20concerns%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20would%20take%20time%20and%20need%20to%20go%20through%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20%26quot%3BSchedule%20F%26quot%3B%20workforce%2C%20which%20allows%20government%20agencies%20to%20reclassify%20workers%20and%20remove%20certain%20protections%20that%20make%20them%20easier%20to%20fire%2C%20could%20mean%20that%20employees%20who%20aren't%20%26quot%3Baligned%20with%20the%20executive%20wholly%26quot%3B%20could%20be%20laid%20off%20based%20on%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20given%20the%20widespread%20denigration%20of%20the%20Education%20Department%20and%20return-to-office%20threats%2C%20people%20are%20likely%20looking%20for%20other%20work.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20be%20surprised%20if%20they%20weren't%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20federal%20worker%20willing%20to%20share%20your%20story%3F%20Contact%20these%20reporters%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaaltcheck%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eaaltcheck%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajkaplan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejkaplan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agweiss%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Egweiss%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-government-efficiency-elon-musk-cuts-worry-federal-workers-layoffs-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732698061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6744e9c6fa0140cdd56553c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-government-efficiency-elon-musk-cuts-worry-federal-workers-layoffs-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20federal%20workers%20are%20worried%2C%20some%20are%20optimistic%2C%20and%20most%20are%20considering%20their%20other%20career%20options%2C%20said%2010%20who%20s