tage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20companies%20have%20very%20large%2C%20highly%20complex%20technical%20architectures%20requiring%20significant%20investment%20and%20time.%20AWS%20wants%20to%20customize%20solutions%20based%20on%20each%20company%20and%20industry%2C%20and%20speed%20up%20deals%20by%20using%20external%20consultants%20and%20partners%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d1a7ea3-fa6a-4a7f-8215-4cc163f8a1b3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Applications%20Acceleration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAWS%20is%20focused%20on%20%26quot%3Bwinning%20the%20largest%20Business%20Application%20providers%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20enterprise%20resource%20planning%20(ERP)%20and%20customer%20relationship%20management%20(CRM)%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20companies%20still%20use%20their%20own%20data%20centers%20to%20run%20business%20applications%20from%20providers%20such%20as%20Salesforce%2C%20Adobe%2C%20and%20ServiceNow.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20wants%20to%20drive%20growth%20by%20getting%20more%20of%20these%20applications%20running%20on%20AWS's%20cloud%2C%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdf5e3c2-fd5a-4d16-96bf-e23f428ea1b3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-Range%20Plan%3A%20Middle%20East%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20lists%20the%20Middle%20East%20market%20as%20one%20of%20the%20top%20business%20opportunities.%20In%20March%2C%20for%20example%2C%20AWS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.aboutamazon.com%2F2024%2F3%2Faws-to-launch-an-infrastructure-region-in-the-kingdom-of-saudi-arabia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20plans%20to%20invest%20more%20than%20%245%20billion%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAWS%20also%20launched%20in%20Bahrain%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20and%20Israel%20in%202019%2C%202022%2C%20and%202023%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIDC%20estimates%20the%20Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20(GCC)%2C%20which%20includes%20Bahrain%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20Oman%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2