r.com%2Felon-musk-government-spending-cut-target-defense-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20failed%20its%20seventh%20audit%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20F-35%20has%20had%20many%20problems.%20It%20suffered%20setbacks%20in%20development%2C%20and%20it%20continues%20to%20face%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-f-35-stealth-fighters-to-fly-less-costs-soar-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20overruns%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff35-fighters-mission-capable-just-over-half-the-time-watchdog-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereadiness%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20availability%20declining%20even%20as%20the%20program%20costs%20rise.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20a%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gao.gov%2Fblog%2Ff-35-will-now-exceed-2-trillion-military-plans-fly-it-less%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatchdog%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20the%20program%20will%20cost%20over%20%242%20trillion%20over%20its%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20posts%20on%20X%20this%20week%2C%20Musk%20sharply%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-f35-idiots-building-unmanned-jets-drone-warfare-doge-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriticized%20both%20the%20stealth%20fighter%20jet%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2C%20indirectly%2C%20its%20manufacturer%3A%20US%20defense%20giant%20Lockheed%20Martin.%20He%20said%20drones%20can%20now%20replicate%20the%20effect%20of%20crewed%20aircraft%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1861070432377737269%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20F-35%20fighter's%20design%20%26quot%3Bwas%20broken%20at%20the%20requirements%20level%20because%20it%20was%20required%20to%20be%20too%20many%20things%20to%20too%20many%20people.%20This%20ma