y%20moving%20toward%20the%20same%20goal%20in%20corporate%20activities%20in%202050.%20To%20further%20this%20goal%2C%20the%20brand%20will%20also%20work%20on%20electrifying%20motorcycles.%20The%20introduction%20of%20Activa%20e%3A%20and%20QC1%20are%20the%20first%20models%20in%20the%20country%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal.%20Here%20are%20all%20the%20details%20of%20the%20new%20electric%20scooters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHonda%20Activa%20e%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHonda%20Activa%20e%20comes%20as%20a%20completely%20new%20model%20carrying%20forward%20the%20name%20of%20the%20popular%20ICE%20scooter.%20It%20not%20only%20takes%20the%20name%20of%20the%20scooter%20but%20also%20the%20body%20and%20frame%20of%20its%20ICE%20counterpart.%20However%2C%20the%20styling%20of%20the%20EV%20is%20completely%20different%2C%20following%20a%20rather%20minimalistic%20approach.%20This%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20slightly%20different%20look%20for%20the%20apron%20of%20the%20EV%20housing%20the%20LED%20headlamp%20with%20turn%20indicators%20on%20either%20side.%20The%20brand%20has%20added%20an%20LED%20DRL%20on%20the%20head%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20It%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20small%20floorboard%20with%20a%20long%20seat.%20The%20rear%20end%20of%20the%20bike%20has%20the%20%26quot%3BActiva%20e%3A%26quot%3B%20badge%20integrated%20into%20the%20tail%20lamp%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fauto%2Friver-indie-electric-scooter-updated-priced-at-rs-1-43-lakh-7111028%5C%22%3ERiver%20Indie%20Electric%20Scooter%20Updated%3B%20Priced%20At%C2%A0%E2%82%B9%C2%A01.43%20Lakh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20seat%2C%20the%20Activa%20e%3A%20gets%20a%20swappable%20battery%20setup%20housing%20two%201.5%20kWh%20batteries.%20The%20power%20from%20these%20units%20is%20transferred%20to%20a%20wheel-side%20electric%20motor%2C%20which%20is%20rated%20to%20have%20a%20power%20output%20of%204.2%20kW%20(5.6%20bhp)%20of%20power.%20This%20output%20can%20be