3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20somebody%20would%20stop%20me%20in%20my%20lying%2C%20but%20nobody%20ever%20said%20that%20I%20wasn't%20in%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20court%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stuck%20to%20her%20story%20even%20after%20Paty's%20death.%20Only%20following%20her%20arrest%20and%2030%20hours%20of%20interrogation%20did%20she%20admit%20to%20investigators%20that%20she%20had%20made%20it%20all%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%2C%20whose%20delivery%20in%20court%20was%20matter-of-fact%2C%20showed%20emotion%20only%20when%20she%20talked%20about%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20my%20lies%2C%20none%20of%20us%20would%20be%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20sobbing.%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20my%20father's%20naivete%20and%20kindness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bmy%20father%20says%20you%20must%20always%20respect%20teachers%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20remark%20that%20prompted%20an%20astonished%20%26quot%3Breally%3F%26quot%3B%20interjected%20by%20the%20court's%20presiding%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20was%20sentenced%20to%2018%20months%20of%20probation%20in%20December%202023%20after%20being%20convicted%20of%20slander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaty%20had%20used%20the%20Charlie%20Hebdo%20magazine%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ethics%20class%20to%20discuss%20free%20speech%20laws%20in%20France%2C%20where%20blasphemy%20is%20legal%20and%20cartoons%20mocking%20religious%20figures%20have%20a%20long%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20killing%20took%20place%20just%20weeks%20after%20Charlie%20Hebdo%20republished%20the%20Prophet%20Mohammed%20cartoons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20magazine%20used%20the%20images%20in%202015%2C%20Islamist%20gunmen%20stormed%20its%20offices%2C%20killing%2012%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22