den%20examination%20from%20strategic%20partners%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Adani%20statement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20conglomerate%20had%20earlier%20refuted%20the%20charges%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B.%20The%20group's%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20(CFO)%20Jugeshinder%20Singh%20had%20clarified%20none%20of%20their%2011%20publicly%20listed%20firms%20were%20accused%20of%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESenior%20lawyer%20Mukul%20Rohtagi%20this%20morning%20countered%20the%20misleading%20reports%20about%20the%20US%20indictment%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20five%20charges.%20It%20is%20very%20important%20to%20note%20that%20Count%201%20and%20Count%205%20are%20more%20important%20than%20the%20others.%20But%20neither%20in%20Count%201%20nor%20Count%205%20is%20Mr%20Adani%20or%20his%20nephew%20charged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20a%20chargesheet%2C%20it%20must%20be%20specific%20to%20say%20that%20so%20and%20so%20has%20done%20such%20and%20such%20act%2C%20so%20and%20so%20has%20bribed%20certain%20individuals.%20But%20I%20do%20not%20find%20a%20single%20name%20or%20detail%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20as%20to%20who%20has%20been%20bribed%2C%20in%20what%20manner%2C%20and%20which%20department%20he%20belongs.%20This%20chargesheet%20is%20completely%20silent%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20former%20Attorney%20General%20of%20India.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMahesh%20Jethmalai%2C%20another%20senior%20lawyer%2C%20said%20the%20Congress%20was%20reading%20too%20much%20into%20the%20indictment%20for%20political%20purposes%20and%20must%20put%20out%20credible%20evidence%20of%20wrongdoing%20in%20the%20public.%20He%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20allegations%20and%20said%20it%20was%20an%20attempt%20at%20stopping%20India's%20growth%20story.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20the%20Congress%20puts%20out%20public%20evidence%20of%20wrongdoing%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20any%20JPC%2