20a%20loss%20of%20near%20%2455%20billion%20in%20its%20market%20capitalisation%20across%20its%2011%20listed%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20full%20statement%20by%20Adani%20Group%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BGautam%20Adani%2C%20nephew%20Sagar%20Adani%2C%20and%20senior%20executive%20Vneet%20Jaain%20are%20clear%20of%20any%20Bribery%20charges%20as%20per%20the%20US%20DoJ%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20filing%20with%20the%20stock%20exchanges%20by%20a%20group%20company-Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd.%20(AGEL).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20its%20filing%2C%20AGEL%20has%20cited%20the%20news%20reporting%20by%20various%20media%20houses%20on%20the%20bribery%20and%20corruption%20charges%20against%20Adani%20Officials%20as%20'Incorrect'.%20%26quot%3BMedia%20articles%20which%20state%20that%20certain%20of%20our%20directors%20namely%20Mr.%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Mr.%20Sagar%20Adani%20and%20Mr.%20Vneet%20Jaain%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20violation(s)%20of%20the%20US%20Foreign%20Corrupt%20Practices%20Act%20(FCPA)%20in%20the%20indictment.%20Such%20statements%20are%20incorrect.%26quot%3B%20Said%20the%20statement%20filed%20by%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20Ltd.%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Mr.%20Sagar%20Adani%20and%20Mr.%20Vneet%20Jaain%20have%20not%20been%20charged%20with%20any%20violation%20of%20the%20FCPA%20in%20the%20counts%20set%20forth%20in%20the%20indictment%20of%20the%20US%20DOJ%20or%20civil%20complaint%20of%20the%20US%20SEC%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontinue-to-believe-in-all-adani-companies-well-positioned-for-future-top-investment-firm-gqg-backs-adani-group-7102362%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWell-Positioned%20For%20Future%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Investment%20Firm%20GQG%20Backs%20Adani%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%2