20his%20nephew%20Sagar%20Adani%20have%20not%20been%20accused%20of%20bribery%20or%20obstructing%20justice%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0The%20senior%20lawyer%20addressed%20the%20media%20to%20counter%20misleading%20news%20reports%20on%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20outset%2C%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20these%20are%20my%20personal%20legal%20views.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20I%20am%20a%20lawyer.%20I%20have%20been%20appearing%20for%20the%20Adani%20Group%20in%20several%20cases.%20I%20have%20gone%20through%20this%20indictment%20by%20the%20US%20court.%20There%20are%20five%20charges.%20It%20is%20very%20important%20to%20note%20that%20Count%201%20and%20Count%205%20are%20more%20important%20than%20the%20others.%20But%20neither%20in%20Count%201%20nor%20Count%205%20is%20Mr%20Adani%20or%20his%20nephew%20charged.%20This%20is%20like%20a%20chargesheet%20that%20charges%20individuals%20for%20specific%20acts.%20Count%201%20is%20against%20certain%20other%20persons%20minus%20the%20two%20Adanis.%20It%20includes%20some%20officers%20and%20one%20foreign%20person.%20The%20first%20allegation%20is%20there%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20violate%20the%20(US)%20Foreign%20Corrupt%20Practices%20Act.%20In%20that%2C%20the%20Adanis%20are%20not%20named%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rohatgi%20said%20the%20Adanis%20and%20others%20are%20named%20in%20counts%20relating%20to%20securities%20and%20bonds.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Count%205%2C%20which%20relates%20to%20obstruction%20of%20justice%2C%20the%20Adanis%20and%20their%20officers%20are%20not%20named.%20The%20Adanis%20and%20others%20will%20respond%20to%20this%20chargesheet%20in%20the%20manner%20that%20they%20desire%2C%20they%20will%20also%20respond%20to%20stock%20exchanges.%20These%20are%20my%20personal%20views%20after%20taking%20a%20look%20at%20this%20chargesheet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rohatgi%20then%20mentioned%20something%20%26quot%3Btroubling%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20indictment%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20look%20at%20a%20chargesheet%2C%20it%20must%20be%20specific%20to%20say%20that%20so%20and%20so%20has%20done%20such%20and%20such%20act%2C%20so%20and%20so%20has%20bribed%20certain%20individuals.%20But%20I%20do%20not%20find%20a%20single%20name%20or%20detail%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20as%20to%20who%20has%20been%20bribed%2C%20in%20what%20manner%2C%20and%20which%20department%20he%20belongs.%20This%20chargesheet%20is%20completely%20silent.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20one%20can%20respond%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20chargesheet.%20But%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20Adanis%20will%20take%20legal%20opinion%20from%20US%20lawyers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rohatgi%20later%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20charges%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20specific%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20written%20who%20was%20bribed%2C%20how%20much%20bribe%20was%20paid%20and%20which%20contract%20it%20was%20paid%20for.%20I%20can't%20say%20if%20they%20will%20share%20more%20information%20later%2C%20but%20these%20papers%20have%20no%20mention%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20bribe%20or%20who%20it%20was%20paid%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732682160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fvus80rc8_mukul-rohatgi_625x300_27_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-detail-in-chargesheet-over-who-has-been-bribed-senior-lawyer-mukul-rohatgi-on-us-charges-against-adani-group-7115038%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20detail%20in%20chargesheet%20over%20who%20has%20been%20bribed%26quot%3B%3A%20Senior%20lawyer%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%20on%20US%20charges%20against%20Adani%20Group%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%