pect.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBurke%20Ramsey%20was%209%20years%20old%20when%20his%20family%20was%20thrust%20into%20the%20spotlight%20after%20his%20younger%20sister%2C%20JonBen%C3%A9t%20Ramsey%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20Boulder%2C%20Colorado%2C%20home%20on%20December%2026%2C%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shocking%20and%20brutal%20nature%20of%20the%20killing%20(the%206-year-old%20was%20found%20with%20a%20strangulation%20device%20called%20a%20garrote%20embedded%20in%20her%20neck%3B%20an%20autopsy%20later%20revealed%20that%20her%20skull%20had%20been%20fractured)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfamous-crimes-from-1990s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincited%20a%20media%20frenzy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20strange%20details%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-cold-cases-true-crime-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill-unsolved%20murder%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20ransom%20note%20left%20behind%20that%20claimed%20JonBen%C3%A9t%20had%20been%20kidnapped%20and%20demanded%20%24118%2C000%20for%20her%20return%2C%20when%20her%20body%20had%20been%20in%20the%20home%20all%20along%20%E2%80%94%20have%20led%20true-crime%20fans%20to%20spend%20the%20ensuing%20decades%20poring%20over%20the%20case%20and%20forming%20their%20own%20theories%20about%20what%20really%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20came%20to%20believe%20that%20someone%20in%20the%20Ramsey%20family%20was%20responsible%20for%20JonBen%C3%A9t's%20death%3B%20they%20weren't%20formally%20cleared%20as%20suspects%20until%202008.%20A%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20docuseries%2C%20%26quot%3BCold%20Case%3A%20Who%20Killed%20JonBen%C3%A9t%20Ramsey%3F%26quot%3B%20explores%20how%20the%20initial%20investigation%20was%20faulty%20and%20accuses%20the%20original%20Boulder%20investigators%2C%20along%20with%20the%20media%2C%20of%20unfairly%20pointing%20suspicion%20toward%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20think%20of%20another%20family%20that's%20been%20so%20brutalized%20so%20unfairly%20by%20the%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20director%20Joe%20Berlinger%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20ahead%20of%20the%20docuseries'%20premiere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurke%20Ramsey%20became%20(and%20remains)%20a%20particular%20target%20of%20suspicion%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-killed-jonbenet-ramsey-theories-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJonBen%C3%A9t%20theorists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20participate%20in%20the%20new%20Netflix%20docuseries.%20Here's%20what%20we%20know%20about%20Burke's%20life%20since%20his%20sister's%20murder%20and%20where%20he%20is%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f847982f-be64-40de-bf64-5aee043d41fd%5C%22%3ETheories%20that%20Burke%20Ramsey%20killed%20his%20sister%20JonBen%C3%A9t%20led%20to%20legal%20action%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Patsy%2C%20JonBenet%2C%20Burke%2C%20and%20John%20Ramsey%20in%20a%20family%20photo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6746407b9f2901eb6037251c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatsy%2C%20JonBenet%2C%20Burke%2C%20and%20John%20Ramsey%20in%20a%20family%20photo.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Netflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBurke%2C%20along%20with%20his%20parents%2C%20moved%20back%20to%20Atlanta%2C%20where%20the%20family%20had%20lived%20before%20Boulder%2C%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-casting-jonbenet-review-sundance-2017-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJonBen%C3%A9t's%20death%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20Patsy%20and%20John%20Ramsey%20continued%20to%20do%20interviews%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20combat%20the%20suspicion%20against%20them%20and%20encouraged%20authorities%20to%20keep%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20Burke%2C%20then%20still%20a%20child%2C%20kept%20out%20of%20the%20spotlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20the%20Boulder%20District%20Attorney's%20Office%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.denverpost.com%2F2008%2F07%2F09%2Fda-clears-ramsey-family%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficially%20cleared%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Ramsey%20family%20(including%20Burke%20and%20Patsy%2C%20who'd%20died%20two%20years%20earlier)%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-conspiracy-theories-2017-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJonBen%C3%A9t's%20murder%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20confirming%20with%20new%20testing%20that%20male%20DNA%20found%20on%20the%20child's%20underwear%20didn't%20match%20anyone%20in%20the%20family.%20Then-DA%20Mary%20Lacy%20also%20apologized%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20John%20Ramsey%20for%20the%20possibility%20that%20her%20office%20had%20contributed%20to%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20perception%20that%20you%20might%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20this%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20clear%20the%20Ramsey%20family%20publicly%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fda-opens-cleared-ramsey-family-jonbenets-murder%2Fstory%3Fid%3D43106426%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtroversial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20in%20the%20event%20of%20new%20DNA%20testing%2C%20as%20the%20Ramsey%20family%20and%20the%20Netflix%20docuseries%20are%20pushing%20for%2C%20all%20previously%20cleared%20suspects%20should%20be%20reconsidered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.dailycamera.com%2Fextra%2Framsey%2F1999%2F20crmsy.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaily%20Camera%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Boulder%20newspaper%2C%20Burke%20had%20been%20interviewed%20by%20investigators%20at%20least%20three%20times%20and%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.dailycamera.com%2Fextra%2Framsey%2F1999%2F52699crams.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappeared%20before%20the%20grand%20jury%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20investigated%20the%20case%20in%201999.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Boulder%20District%20Attorney's%20office%20said%20Burke%20had%20never%20been%20under%20suspicion.%20(As%20the%20Netflix%20doc%20recounts%2C%20court%20documents%20unsealed%20in%202013%20later%20revealed%20that%20the%20grand%20jury%20had%20voted%20to%20indict%20John%20and%20Patsy%20Ramsey%20on%20two%20counts%20each%20of%20child%20abuse%20resulting%20in%20JonBen%C3%A9t's%20death%2C%20though%20then-DA%20Alex%20Hunter%20chose%20not%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20the%20indictment%20because%20he%20said%20the%20evidence%20wasn't%20sufficient%20to%20prosecute%20them.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202016%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%2020th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20crime%2C%20CBS%20aired%20the%20docuseries%20%26quot%3BThe%20Case%20of%3A%20JonBen%C3%A9t%20Ramsey.%26quot%3B%20In%20it%2C%20a%20group%20that%20included%20former%20FBI%20agents%2C%20a%20forensic%20scientist%2C%20and%20a%20forensic%20pathologist%20reevaluated%20the%20evidence%20and%20theorized%20that%20Burke%20had%20killed%20JonBen%C3%A9t%2C%20likely%20accidentally%2C%20by%20striking%20her%20over%20the%20head%20after%20she%20took%20a%20piece%20of%20pineapple%20from%20his%20bowl%20and%20that%20their%20parents%20had%20written%20the%20ransom%20note%20to%20cover%20up%20how%20JonBen%C3%A9t%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurke's%20attorneys%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fbrother-jonbenet-ramsey-sues-cbs-750m-over-series-n701006%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20defamation%20lawsuits%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20network%2C%20producers%2C%20and%20the%20series'%20hosts%20for%20%24750%20million%20later%20that%20year%3B%20he'd%20separately%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjonbent-ramsey-brother-burke-lawsuit-cbs-special-2016-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20another%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20one%20of%20t