%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFarez%20Najid%20is%20a%20professional%20%26quot%3BD%26amp%3BD%26quot%3B%20dungeon%20master%20who%20first%20entered%20the%20business%20after%20being%20inspired%20by%20Critical%20Role.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFarez%20Najid%20turned%20his%20Dungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons%20hobby%20into%20a%20thriving%20business%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInspired%20by%20Critical%20Role%2C%20Najid%20and%20his%20partners%20opened%20a%20studio%20for%20paid%20D%26amp%3BD%20games%20in%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20business%20now%20includes%20multiple%20locations%2C%20a%20retail%20space%2C%20and%20a%20dungeon%20master%20training%20program.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Farez%20Najid%2C%20a%20professional%20%26quot%3BDungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons%26quot%3B%20dungeon%20master%20and%20the%20co-owner%20of%20the%20TableMinis%20Tabletop%20Roleplaying%20Game%20Studio%20in%20Singapore.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20employment%20history.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20height%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20came%20together%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20of%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20working%20in%20the%20Singaporean%20theater%20business%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20when%20live%20performances%20ground%20to%20a%20standstill%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20idea%20hit%20me%3A%20I'd%20been%20watching%20a%20Twitch-based%20show%20called%20Critical%20Role%20for%20years%2C%20where%20a%20group%20of%20voice%20actors%20sit%20around%20the%20table%20playing%20%26quot%3BDungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons%26quot%3B%20live.%20It%20was%20enthralling%20to%20watch%20the%20show's%20eight%20co-founders%20as%20they%20found%20a%20way%20to%20convert%20their%20home%20game%20into%20a%20streaming%20hit%20and%20a%20business%20in%20its%20own%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20people%20are%20my%20heroes.%20And%20the%20idea%20that%20someone%20could%20convert%20their%20nerdy%20hobby%20into%20a%20career%20inspired%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wondered%20%E2%80%94%20what%20if%20I%20could%20make%20a%20career%20out%20of%20%26quot%3BD%26amp%3BD%26quot%3B%20too%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20Farez%20Najid%20with%20his%20green%20dragon%20miniature%2C%20and%20a%20picture%20of%20Najid's%20dice%20collection.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674588c8ede4eeae392985b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20have%20everything%20I%20need%20in%20my%20studio%2C%20from%20sprawling%20battle%20maps%20and%20ferocious%20dragon%20miniatures%20to%20an%20extensive%20dice%20collection.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20business%20partners%2C%20Jodie%20Yeo%20and%20Dennet%20Krishnan%2C%20took%20a%20chance%20on%20the%20wild%20idea%20that%20we%20could%20set%20up%20a%20small%20studio%20and%20run%20paid%20%26quot%3BDungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons%26quot%3B%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20that%20works.%20Some%20%26quot%3BD%26amp%3BD%26quot%3B%20fans%20may%20be%20looking%20for%20other%20folks%20to%20play%20the%20game%20with%20and%20a%20comfortable%20space%20to%20play%20it%20in%20at%20an%20affordable%20rate.%20Others%20are%20looking%20for%20experienced%20dungeon%20masters%20%E2%80%94%20the%20people%20responsible%20for%20crafting%20the%20game%20narrative.%20Games%20can%20be%20one-shots%20spanning%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20or%20multi-game%20campaigns%2C%20not%20unlike%20those%20you%20see%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-role-dungeons-dragons-sold-out-live-show-wembley-arena-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECritical%20Role%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-dimension-20-dropout-built-nerdworld-empire-madison-square-garden-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDimension%2020%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20started%20out%20in%20April%202021%2C%20we%20had%20%24500%20Singapore%20dollars%20(or%20%24370)%20in%20capital%20and%20operated%20out%20of%20a%20single-room%20studio.%20We%20ran%20five%20games%20weekly%2C%20charging%20people%20%2430%20per%20person.%20That%20meant%20that%20a%20table%20of%20five%20could%20net%20me%20around%20%24150.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helped%20that%20I'd%20started%20running%20paid%20games%20online%20at%20%2425%20per%20head%20while%20we%20were%20in%20the%20pandemic%20lockdown.%20We%20began%20to%20get%20more%20bookings%2C%20and%20the%20single-room%20studio%20space%20wasn't%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20months%2C%20we%20opened%20a%20second%20and%20third%20game%20room.%20We%20then%20realized%20we%20were%20getting%20way%20too%20many%20bookings%20to%20keep%20it%20limited%20to%20three%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20moved%20to%20our%20current%20location%20at%20Arumugam%20Road%20in%20April%202023.%20It%20has%20four%20separate%20gaming%20spaces%2C%20including%20a%20staging%20area%20complete%20with%20a%20projector%20and%20equipment%20%E2%80%94%20where%20people%20can%20play%20their%20games%20live%20for%20an%20audience%2C%20Critical%20Role-style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20me%20that%20players%20are%20immersed%20in%20the%20game%20and%20feel%20safe%20and%20included%20at%20my%20table.%20That%20means%20pulling%20out%20all%20the%20stops%2C%20with%20custom%20terrain%20for%20games.%20It%20means%20being%20educated%20about%20gaming%20best%20practices%20and%20being%20as%20good%20a%20listener%20as%20you%20are%20a%20storyteller.%20It%20also%20means%20a%20full%20day%20of%20prep%20and%20set-up%20before%20a%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20of%20Najid%20dungeon-mastering%20for%20a%20party%20at%20TableMinis%2C%20Arumugam%20Road.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67458952ede4eeae392985be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESetting%20up%20and%20preparing%20for%20a%20game%20can%20take%20an%20entire%20day%2C%20but%20I%20find%20it%20rewarding.%3Cp%3ECheryl%20Teh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20make%20sure%20I%20have%20all%20my%20non-player%20characters%20prepped%2C%20and%20I%20review%20my%20notes%20again%20to%20ensure%20my%20storytelling%20is%20solid.%20I%20also%20take%20time%20to%20set%20up%20things%20like%20battle%20maps%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20table%20%E2%80%94%20we%20have%20equipment%20from%20terrain%20tiles%20and%20monstrous%20miniatures%20that%20I%20get%20to%20play%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20a%20proper%20studio%20space%2C%20too%2C%20has%20improved%20the%20player%20experience.%20We%20have%20rooms%20that%20we%20try%20to%20soundproof%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20so%20the%20noise%20from%20one%20game%20doesn't%20filter%20into%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20community%20space%20outside%20our%20main%20studio%2C%20where%20people%20can%20hang%20out%20before%20and%20after%20their%20%26quot%3BD%26amp%3BD%26quot%3B%20games.%20And%20there's%20a%20retail%20space%20where%20people%20can%20pick%20up%20merchandise%20like%20dice%20and%20miniatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20I%20still%20run%20games%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I've%20limited%20it%20to%20a%20yearlong%20campaign%20for%20a%20small%20group%20of%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20more%20focused%20on%20the%20business%20development%20aspect%20of%20TableMinis%20%E2%80%94%20because%20the%20business%20is%20now%20bigger%20than%20me.%20With%20our%20Chinatown%20outlet%20that%20opened%20in%20September%2C%20we%20now%20have%20two%20separate%20studio%20locations%20that%20can%20run%20multiple%20games%20per%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20started%20training%20new%20game%20masters%20un