blished%22%3A1732647077000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fbd27%2Flive%2F40f3b470-ac27-11ef-a4fe-a3e9a6c5d640.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcgl4wy7lyzyo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22His%20announcement%20comes%20after%20more%20than%20a%20year%20of%20conflict%20between%20Israeli%20and%20Hezbollah%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcgl4wy7lyzyo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bajrang%20Punia%20Suspended%20For%20Four%20Years%20By%20National%20Anti-Doping%20Body%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Anti-Doping%20Agency%20on%20Tuesday%20suspended%20Bajrang%20Punia%20for%20four%20years%20for%20his%20refusal%20to%20provide%20his%20sample%20for%20dope%20test%20on%20March%2010%20during%20selection%20trials%20for%20the%20national%20team.%20NADA%20had%20first%20suspended%20the%20Tokyo%20Games%20bronze%20medallist%20wrestler%20on%20April%2023%20for%20the%20offence%20following%20which%2C%20the%20World%20Governing%20body%20UWW%20had%20also%20suspended%20him.%20Bajrang%20had%20appealed%20against%20the%20provisional%20suspension%20and%20NADA's%20Anti-Disciplinary%20Doping%20panel%20(ADDP)%20had%20revoked%20it%20on%20May%2031%20till%20NADA%20issues%20the%20notice%20of%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENADA%2C%20then%20on%20June%2023%20served%20the%20notice%20to%20the%20wrestler.%20Bajrang%2C%20who%20joined%20Congress%20along%20with%20fellow%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20was%20given%20charge%20of%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Congress%2C%20had%20challenged%20the%20charge%20on%20July%2011%20in%20a%20written%20submission%20following%20which%20hearings%20were%20held%20on%20September%2020%20and%20October%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Panel%20holds%20that%20the%20Athlete%20is%20liable%20for%20sanctions%20under%20Article%2010.3.1%20and%20liable%20for%20ineligibility%20for%20a%20period%20of%204%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ADDP%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20means%20that%20Bajrang%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20return%20to%20competitive%20wrestling%20and%20apply%20for%20a%20coaching%20job%20abroad%2C%20if%20he%20aspires%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20present%20case%2C%20since%20the%20Athlete%20had%20been%20provisionally%20suspended%2C%20the%20Panel%20accordingly%20holds%20that%20the%20Athlete's%20period%20of%20his%20ineligibility%20for%20the%20period%20of%204%20years%20shall%20commence%20from%20the%20date%20on%20which%20the%20notification%20was%20sent%2C%20i.e.%2C%2023.04.2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeedless%20to%20say%20that%20on%20account%20of%20the%20lifting%20of%20the%20provisional%20suspension%20for%20the%20period%20from%2031.05.2024%20to%2021.06.2024%20shall%20not%20be%20credited%20into%20the%20total%20period%20of%20ineligibility%20of%20four%20years.%26quot%3B%20Bajrang%20has%20maintained%20since%20the%20beginning%20that%20he%20was%20given%20extremely%20prejudicial%20and%20unfair%20treatment%20with%20respect%20to%20doping%20control%20because%20of%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20protest%20against%20former%20WFI%20President%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrang%20also%20maintained%20that%20he%20never%20refused%20to%20give%20sample%20but%20only%20demanded%20to%20know%20NADA's%20response%20to%20his%20email%20where%20he%20sought%20answer%20why%20expired%20kits%20were%20sent%20to%20take%20his%20samples%20in%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENADA%20also%20explained%20the%20reason%20for%20its%20action%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Chaperone%2FDCO%20had%20duly%20approached%20him%20and%20informed%20that%20he%20was%20required%20to%20provide%20a%20urine%20sample%20for%20dope%20analysis%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrang%20in%20his%20written%20submission%20said%20that%20the%20conduct%20of%20NADA%20in%20two%20previous%20instances%20had%20created%20mistrust%20in%20the%20athlete's%20mind%2C%20especially%20with%20NADA%20failing%20to%20acknowledge%20or%20even%20respond%20to%20their%20callous%20approach%20towards%20the%20doping%20control%20process%20in%20both%20such%20instances%2C%20the%20failure%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20their%20action%20pertaining%20to%20their%20dispersal%20of%20duties%20meant%20that%20the%20athlete%20was%20morally%20bound%20to%20take%20a%20stance%20in%20resort%20as%20a%20senior%20athlete%20who%20holds%20a%20voice%20in%20the%20sporting%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajrang%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20not%20an%20outright%20refusal%20per%20se.%20The%20athlete%20was%20always%20willing%20to%20provide%20his%20sample%20provided%20that%20he%20first%20received%20a%20response%20from%20NADA%20concerning%20the%20use%20of%20expired%20kits.%26quot%3B%20However%20NADA%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20outright%20refusal%20by%20the%20athlete%20to%20provide%20urine%20sample%20for%20the%20dope%20test%20was%20intentional%20and%20deliberate%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3BAthlete%20has%20demonstrated%20utter%20disregard%20towards%20his%20duties%20and%20responsibilities%20as%20per%20Articles%2020.1%20%26amp%3B%2020.2%20of%20the%20Anti%20Doping%20Rules%2C%202021.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732644360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Frdmtci1g_bajrang-punia_625x300_03_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fbajrang-punia-suspended-for-four-years-by-national-anti-doping-body-due-to-violation-of-code-7113081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20suspension%20means%20that%20Bajrang%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20return%20to%20competitive%20wrestling%20and%20apply%20for%20a%20coaching%20job%20abroad%2C%20if%20he%2