20%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20concept%20of%20the%20concert%20was%20that%20I%20would%20sing%20for%20an%20hour.%20Many%20musicians%20attended%20this%20concert%2C%20and%20after%20my%20hour-long%20performance%2C%20they%20sang%20a%20set%20of%20compositions%20in%20100%20different%20%3Cem%3Eragas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20had%20to%20identify%20each%20%3Cem%3Eraga%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20I%20did%20successfully.%20This%20concert%20was%20filmed%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20person%20who%20recorded%20it%20lost%20the%20VHS%20tape.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FIaLqkeKx814%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20her%20beginnings%20as%20a%20child%20prodigy%20in%20Carnatic%20music%20to%20recording%20%E2%80%98A%20Rock%20Somewhere%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20inimitable%20Jacob%20Collier%20and%20Anoushka%20Shankar%20%E2%80%94%20nominated%20this%20year%20for%20a%20Grammy%20Award%20for%20%E2%80%98Best%20Global%20Music%20Performance%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Varijashree%20has%20undertaken%20a%20remarkable%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20musician%20with%20a%20classical%20foundation%20who%20has%20since%20expanded%20into%20diverse%20cross-cultural%20and%20inte