20watch%2C%20and%20observe%20how%20they%20not%20only%20performed%20but%20also%20learnt%2C%20practised%2C%20and%20perceived%20art.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20I%20did%20not%20understand%20much%20as%20a%20child%2C%20it%20all%20started%20to%20make%20sense%20when%20I%20began%20to%20grasp%20the%20finer%20nuances%20of%20music%3B%20these%20were%20very%20valuable%20memories%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20child%20prodigy%20comes%20to%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20incredible%20talent%20and%20having%20learnt%20all%20the%20fundamentals%20from%20her%20first%20gurus%2C%20Varijashree%E2%80%99s%20parents%20felt%20it%20was%20best%20to%20enrol%20her%20in%20more%20formal%20and%20focused%20lessons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%20four%2C%20she%20began%20formal%20training%20in%20Carnatic%20vocals%20under%20Vidhushi%20(a%20title%20for%20a%20female%20Carnatic%20classical%20musician)%20H%20Geetha.%20Varijashree%20was%20seven%20when%20she%20gave%20her%20first%20full-fledged%20Carnatic%20vocal%20performance%20at%20the%20Bangalore%20Gayana%20Samaja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20learning%20under%20her%20tutelage%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20I%20also%20learned%20some%20rare%20and%20exclusive%20compositions%20from%20Vidhushi%20Vasantha%20Srinivasan%20and%20Vidwan%20(a%20title%20for%20a%20male%20Carnatic%20musician)%20D%20S%20Srivatsa.%20However%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20my%20formal%20training%20occurred%20under%20Gaanakalanidhi%20Vidwan%20Salem%20P%20Sundaresan.%20I%20was%20fortunate%20to%20have%20him%20as%20my%20guru.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20came%20under%20his%20tutelage%2C%20he%20was%2080%20years%20old.%20An%20ex-bank%20manager%2C%20my%20guru%20was%20an%20encyclopaedia%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F253401%2Fkerala-peruvemba-mridangam-carnatic-music-instrument-kasumani-indian-musicians-family-legacy-history-tradition-culture-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarnatic%20music%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20spent%2015%20years%20of%20intense%20training%20under%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varijashree%20Venugopal%3A%20From%20a%20child%20prodigy%20to%20a%20Grammy%20nomination.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FVarijashree-Image-1-1732544017-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVarijashree%20Venugopal%3A%20From%20a%20child%20prodigy%20to%20a%20Grammy%20nomination.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20picking%20up%20the%20flute%20and%20learning%20how%20to%20play%20it%20formally%20was%20not%20planned.%20According%20to%20her%2C%20it%20just%20happened%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20a%20pleasant%2C%20yet%20accidental%20surprise%20to%20me%20and%20to%20my%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20curious%20about%20the%20instrument%2C%20and%20I%20would%20dabble%20and%20experiment%20with%20it%20in%20between%20my%20ninth%20and%20tenth%20years%20of%20formal%20training.%20Luckily%2C%20I%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20produce%20a%20sound%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20most%20difficult%20part%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20bamboo%20flute.%20I%20had%20also%20secretly%20tried%20learning%20some%20things%20that%20my%20father%20was%20already%20teaching%20other%20students.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20told%20him%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20show%20him%20how%20I%20played%20a%20certain%20composition%20on%20the%20flute.%20To%20his%20surprise%2C%20I%20played%20something%20that%20was%20more%20proficient%20than%20he%20had%20expected.%20So%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20train%20me%20formally.%20Soon%2C%20I%20started%20accompanying%20him%20in%20his%20concerts%2C%20and%20later%20on%2C%20I%20began%20performing%20in%20my%20own%20solo%20flute%20concerts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20playing%20in%20recording%20sessions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarijashree%20was%20just%20about%2014%20years%20old%20when%20she%20began%20accompanying%20her%20father!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoing%20beyond%20the%20world%20of%20Carnatic%20music%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20an%20environment%20steeped%20in%20the%20essence%20of%20Carnatic%20music%2C%20her%20parents%20also%20exposed%20her%20to%20a%20world%20beyond%20it%20through%20audio%20cassette%20tapes.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20used%20to%20play%20audio%20cassettes%20every%20day.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20Carnatic%20music%3B%20they%20also%20played%20Hindustani%20music%20and%20light%20classical%20forms%20like%20%3Cem%3EBhajans%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EAbhang%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fusion%20acts%20like%20Shakti%2C%20John%20McLaughlin%2C%20and%20L%20Shankar.%20These%20were%20some%20of%20the%20initial%20influences%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%2C%20however%2C%20changed%20everything.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20she%20discovered%20a%20wealth%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F54054%2Fjazz-india-1920-bombay-louis-banks-bollywood-bands%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejazz%20music%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20particularly%20artists%20like%20Chick%20Corea%2C%20Miles%20Davis%2C%20John%20Coltrane%2C%20and%20Bobby%20McFerrin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20initially%20drawn%20more%20to%20jazz%20and%20its%20associated%20forms%20because%20of%20the%20improvisational%20space%20it%20offers.%20That%20resonated%20with%20me%20because%20Indian%20classical%20music%20is%20also%20highly%20improvisational%20while%20being%20structured.%20What%20fascinated%20me%20was%20that%20jazz%20improvisations%20are%20not%20confined%20to%20a%20raga%3B%20they%20move%20through%20changing%20tonalities%20and%20explore%20various%20directions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20something%20I%20had%20never%20heard%20before%2C%20and%20it%20prompted%20me%20to%20try%20to%20sing%20those%20elements.%20My%20only%20goal%20was%20to%20see%20if%20I%20could%20emulate%20what%20a%20jazz%20instrumentalist%20or%20vocalist%20was%20performing%2C%20including%20scatting.%20I%20wanted%20to%20experiment%20with%20moving%20my%20vocal%20techniques%20in%20this%20new%20format%2C%20and%20that%20led%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%20and%20experimentation%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20this%20day.%20Every%20new%20piece%20I%20work%20on%20remains%20an%20extension%20of%20that%20exercise%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%