heri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(concert).%20Applying%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20classical%20Carnatic%20music%20in%20a%20global%20context%20has%20enabled%20me%20to%20transcribe%20a%20jazz%20solo%20into%20Indian%20notation%20and%20then%20improvise%20on%20it%20while%20incorporating%20those%20fundamentals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECollaborating%20with%20Jacob%20Collier%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2012%20years%2C%20Varijashree%20has%20worked%20with%20a%20series%20of%20legendary%20Jazz%20artists%20from%20the%20West%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Victor%20Wooten%20and%20Bobby%20McFerrin.%20Working%20in%20these%20spaces%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20tap%20into%20a%20network%20of%20similarly%20talented%20and%20renowned%20artists.%20It%20is%20through%20this%20network%20stretching%20across%20continents%20that%20Jacob%20and%20Varijashree%20got%20to%20know%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20been%20a%20fan%20of%20his%20work.%20Similarly%2C%20one%20of%20my%20videos%20may%20have%20appeared%20on%20his%20radar%2C%20following%20which%20he%20figured%20out%20that%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20common%20friends.%20We%20used%20to%20keep%20in%20touch%20now%20and%20then%20on%20Instagram.%20One%20day%2C%20however%2C%20he%20wrote%20to%20me%20saying%20that%20he%20was%20recording%20the%20fourth%20volume%20of%20Djesse%20(Djesse%20Vol.%204%20album)%20and%20that%20there%20was%20this%20song%20where%20he%20was%20imagining%20my%20voice%20that%20he%20thought%20would%20add%20perfectly%20well%20into%20the%20blend%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_466221808_527686340145671_4005691837502396191_n_1080-1732544376.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varijashree%20with%20Jacob%20Collier%5C%22%20width%3D%